{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775847924305,"sessionID":"ses_2873782adfferdluqTqD82CWpe","part":{"id":"prt_d78c8ded9001x1JdoNV7bzAAsq","messageID":"msg_d78c8c0f9001JG5VIbdYmSB8i7","sessionID":"ses_2873782adfferdluqTqD82CWpe","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-babb5f678ee14dbe899930d2eb7b234a","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-008/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-008/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-008 — Sandbox GC 定时清理机制 Design\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-008 — Sandbox GC 定时清理机制 |\n8: | Module | `pkg/workloadmanager` |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | S |\n11: | Stage | ST-1 |\n12: \n13: [待填写: Sandbox GC 定时清理机制的设计概述]\n14: \n15: ## Design\n16: \n17: ### Architecture\n18: \n19: [待填写: 架构图和组件关系]\n20: \n21: ### Dependencies\n22: \n23: | Package | Purpose |\n24: |---------|---------|\n25: | [待填写] | [待填写] |\n26: \n27: ## Data Structures\n28: \n29: ### Core Types\n30: \n31: [待填写: 核心数据结构定义]\n32: \n33: ## API Endpoints\n34: \n35: [待填写: API 端点定义]\n36: \n37: ## Error Handling\n38: \n39: [待填写: 错误处理策略]\n40: \n41: ## Testing Strategy\n42: \n43: [待填写: 测试策略]\n44: \n45: ## Validation Checklist\n46: \n47: - [ ] [待填写]\n48: \n49: ## Open Questions\n50: \n51: - Q: [待填写]\n52:   - A: [待填写]\n53: \n54: ## References\n55: \n56: - [待填写]\n\n(End of file - total 56 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-008 — Sandbox GC 定时清理机制 Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-008 — Sandbox GC 定时清理机制 |\n| Module | `pkg/workloadmanager` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Stage | ST-1 |\n\n[待填写: Sandbox GC 定时清理机制的设计概述]\n\n## Design\n\n### Architecture\n\n[待填写: 架构图和组件关系]\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-pl